---
<section>
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2 class="section-title">Who it's for</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Teams that need one control plane for agent access, tool inventory, and policy enforcement.</p>
    <ul class="audience-list">
      <li class="card audience-item">
        <div class="audience-icon icon-magenta">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M9 21V9h6v12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="audience-text">
          <strong>Platform Teams</strong>
          <span>Standardize MCP access, gateway rollout, and policy distribution across local and remote tool servers. Terraform and Helm for infrastructure-as-code deployment.</span>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="card audience-item">
        <div class="audience-icon icon-cyan">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/><polyline points="9 12 11 14 15 10"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="audience-text">
          <strong>Security Teams</strong>
          <span>Fail-closed controls, topology drift detection, injection scanning, supply chain verification, and auditable approvals before risky tool execution.</span>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="card audience-item">
        <div class="audience-icon icon-magenta">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="8" rx="2" ry="2"/><rect x="2" y="14" width="20" height="8" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="6.01" y2="6"/><line x1="6" y1="18" x2="6.01" y2="18"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="audience-text">
          <strong>Agent Builders</strong>
          <span>SDKs for Python, TypeScript, Go, and Java with built-in integrations for LangChain, CrewAI, OpenAI Agents, Google ADK, and Claude Agent.</span>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="card audience-item">
        <div class="audience-icon icon-cyan">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="audience-text">
          <strong>GRC &amp; Compliance</strong>
          <span>Controls mapped to 12 frameworks including EU AI Act, NIS2, DORA, ISO 42001. Evidence packs, gap analysis, and cross-regulation incident reporting.</span>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .audience-list{list-style:none;margin-top:2rem;display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr));gap:1rem}
  .audience-item{padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start}
  .audience-icon{width:44px;height:44px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    border-radius:.5rem;flex-shrink:0}
  .audience-text{display:flex;flex-direction:column}
  .audience-text strong{display:block;margin-bottom:.25rem;color:var(--text)}
  .audience-text span{font-size:.85rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.5}
</style>
